description: When Jordan & Momo met in Japan, it became crystal clear that they were meant to do great things together. Along with snowboarding, traveling the world, and workin’ hard, they also run Miso Hungry, Vermont’s most favorite Ramen spot. Their menu features local favorites, like Roasted Sesame Ramen Salad (with Momo’s secret roasted sesame dressing, baby arugula, crisp mixed peppers, sun burst cherry tomatoes, chilled red onions, and a marinated soft-boiled egg), Spicy Ramen, Gyoza, and more- all made with locally sourced and authentic ingredients, all delicious. So, if “Miso Hungry”, then you so lucky, because this special food truck is serving up satisfying scrumptiousness.
name: Miso Hungry Authentic Japanese Ramen
